{"tid":1520944,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"胡錫進︰路透假新聞圖煽動示威者對抗中央","createTime":"2019-08-31T04:06:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T07:39:20.000Z","uid":39464,"like":17,"dislike":154,"uniUserReply":89,"replies":[{"pid":"b0a2566973f5a8a055ad1a41ab1df42237109389","tid":1520944,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T04:06:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2019/08/31/2237056_4d2ec56723950ee799de748fe5f77a52.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2019%2F08%2F31%2F2237056_4d2ec56723950ee799de748fe5f77a52.jpg&h=cdfaafea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n路透早前報道，特首林鄭月娥曾向北京提交報告，表示撤回修例有助化解政治危機，惟最終被北京拒絕。<br />\n<br />\n《環球時報》總編輯胡錫進在微博發文，指經向官方權威人士了解，這完全是一則假新聞，批評路透用假新聞挑撥中央與香港特區政府的關係，直斥是一次無恥的輿論戰。<br />\n<br />\n胡錫進指出，這篇報道利用一些現實存在的公開活動，比如把這則假新聞與8月7日在深圳召開的香港局勢真座談會編織在一起，又質疑3個所謂不具名消息來源是編造出來的，或者他們是假新聞的合謀者。<br />\n<br />\n文章認為，這則假新聞顯然是要挑撥離間，破壞中央和特區政府的關係，動搖特區政府和香港警隊依法履責的決心，衝擊從香港一線直到國家大後方共同遏制香港騷亂的陣線，這是一些境外勢力很希望嘗試去做的。<br />\n<br />\n此外，他又稱，8月31日全國人大發布關於普選問題的決定5周年紀念日，這條新聞在這個時間被拋出，煽動激進示威者更明確地對抗中央，推動香港當前的騷亂在政治指向上進一步升級。<br />\n<br />\n胡錫進亦批評路透嚴重背離新聞行業道德底線，懷疑這則假新聞就是情報機構的借殼行動，路透做了它們的幫凶。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2237056/%E8%83%A1%E9%8C%AB%E9%80%B2%3A%E8%B7%AF%E9%80%8F%E5%81%87%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E5%9C%96%E7%85%BD%E5%8B%95%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E5%B0%8D%E6%8A%97%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2237056%2F%25E8%2583%25A1%25E9%258C%25AB%25E9%2580%25B2%253A%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E9%2580%258F%25E5%2581%2587%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%25E5%259C%2596%25E7%2585%25BD%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%258A%2597%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25AE&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2SHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=690cd88e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2237056/%E8%83%A1%E9%8C%AB%E9%80%B2%3A%E8%B7%AF%E9%80%8F%E5%81%87%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E5%9C%96%E7%85%BD%E5%8B%95%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E5%B0%8D%E6%8A%97%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE</a>"},{"pid":"4797a0ef2aac6deed028be2df36fa2bd9120af45","tid":1520944,"uid":275243,"like":155,"dislike":2,"score":153,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T04:07:30.000Z","msg":"環時話路透作新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6a7853eabe26003a4372f9d1bd8e6b2753a9e46","tid":1520944,"uid":15605,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T04:08:21.000Z","msg":"割到爛"},{"pid":"fc7086db5a2f374f298b25fb74da222df321cb97","tid":1520944,"uid":172599,"like":22,"dislike":7,"score":15,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T04:09:25.000Z","msg":"1步笑10000步"},{"pid":"0e0ea48b9df3551e0e095ad7c57cbbbede81107a","tid":1520944,"uid":63045,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T04:11:03.000Z","msg":"咩最後一戰呀？明明就係無限之戰，你對手係赤納粹，有二三十年要捱<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1519888\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1519888</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n今日關鍵係人數，唔係勇武"},{"pid":"86614bb038687e94650d90349609861e309d5b58","tid":1520944,"uid":131842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T04:11:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0caac705c83acaba7aa01ac80bde7bc16921d28e","tid":1520944,"uid":36673,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"quote":{"pid":"4797a0ef2aac6deed028be2df36fa2bd9120af45","tid":1520944,"uid":275243,"like":155,"di